==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Kell
<hw>Kell</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[A modification of
<ets>kale</ets>.]</ety> <def>A sort of pottage; kale. See <er>Kale</er>,
2.</def> <rj><au>Ainsworth.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
